{
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "你的坐骑散发着令人不悦的干涸气息。说明来意吧，商人，你打算交易什么筹码？",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "嘿嘿，尊贵的客人！来看看这几件古董吧，绝对物超所值！",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "潮湿的贵客，我们又见面了！这家伙一闻到丰富的水汽就知道是你。",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "快来看看我刚搜罗来的新货吧，这次保证有能入您法眼的稀罕宝贝！",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "回应",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "它的嗅觉依旧敏锐，但愿你今日的商品也能具备同等的价值。\n[i][font_size=22]那维莱特微微欠身，静静审视着散落的物件。[/font_size][/i]",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "DARV.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "哈哈，包您满意！这几件可是尖货，挑一件吧！",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "不必干预，庞大的生灵，水元素的潮汐自会为我重塑形体。",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "[sine]...尊贵的... ..源海之主..... ...您的... 大权.... 压迫着... ..我的... 呼吸.....[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "[sine]...再次... 迎接您... \n..尊贵的... 掌水者......[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "[sine]...请收下... 这份... 卑微的... 祝福......[/sine]",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "回应",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "感谢你的善意与馈赠。若前方确有违逆公正之事，我自会践行审判的职责。",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NEOW.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "[sine]...去吧... \n...让纯净的... 波涛... 淹没... 罪恶......[/sine]",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "这位女士，您周身萦绕着深海的湿润气息。\n不知拦下我的脚步，有何见教？",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "多么迷人的高贵气质！收下这些璀璨的首饰与华服吧，它们正配您的优雅呢。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "啊，高贵的先生，我们又在潮湿的洋流中重逢了。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "快来看看我新寻得的珍宝，只有您的气质才配得上它们的光芒。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "婉拒",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "您的慷慨如纯净的泉水般令人感怀。不过华服与珍饰……于我而言只需得体便好。",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "NONUPEIPE.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "呵呵，您太谦虚了，快挑一件吧，让这座高塔见证您的绝代风华！",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "真是令人赞叹的生命形态。你的目光中毫无杂念，唯有如同清澈泉水般纯粹的好奇心。",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "水！好多水！从海里来！？快讲讲海里的故事！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "水里来的朋友！又见面啦！！上次的故事没听够！还要听！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "快讲快讲！神奇的冒险！我准备了好多亮闪闪的东西换！！",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "回应",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "既然你如此期盼。那便讲一个美露莘与画笔的故事吧，它如晨露般纯挚。",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "OROBAS.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "哇！！美露莘好可爱！太棒了！！这些亮闪闪都给你！！",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "同属龙脉，你的身躯却如消融的冰雪。愿这纯净的水元素，能为你带来片刻的安宁。",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "[thinky_dots]水流的触感……让人安心。收下我的这份血肉吧，朋友……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "[thinky_dots]欢迎回来，朋友……你身上那种令人安心的强大，真像我的父亲……[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "[thinky_dots]既然你拥有如此伟岸的力量……如果在前方遇到他，能请你帮帮他吗？[/thinky_dots]",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "回答",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "我会探明前路的真相，若确有需要纠正的偏颇，我定会秉公裁决。",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "PAEL.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "[thinky_dots]谢谢……带走这块血肉吧，我要在无梦的睡眠中，等待焕然一新……[/thinky_dots]",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "阁下体内充斥着狂躁的气息。在攀登高塔的途中，我无意挑起无谓的争端。",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "[b]好惊人的压迫感！你绝对是个真正的强者！拿着这把武器，快和我痛快地打一场！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "[b]上次居然敢拒绝战斗！这次我绝不让你逃跑！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "[b]快拿出你真正的实力，让我们痛痛快快地打一场！！！[/b]",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "应允",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "既然纯粹的言语无法平息你的躁动，那便以绝对的力量对你进行威慑吧。\n[i][font_size=22]那维莱特轻松制服了坦克斯。[/font_size][/i]",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TANX.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "[b]太强了！我输得心服口服！这把武器归你了，我们下次再战！！！[/b]",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "在这漫长的旅途中，您身旁的火焰透着令人安心的暖意。\n向您致敬，女士。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "哎呀，多么强大却又疲惫的灵魂！快靠近些亲爱的，让特兹卡塔拉来[jitter][b]温暖[/b][/jitter]你。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "带着水汽的小可爱，欢迎回来！快坐下歇歇脚吧。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "特兹卡塔拉刚做好了[jitter][b]点心[/b][/jitter]哦，快来陪我吃一点，别总是把自己绷得那么紧呀。",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "推辞",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "感谢好意，但我通常只需纯净之水……",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "TEZCATARA.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "放心吧亲爱的，特意为你准备了饱含丰沛果汁的做法，一点都不干，快尝尝！",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.char": "阁下言语间充斥着诱导与浑浊的恶意。若再试图引诱无辜者滑向深渊，我将亲自降下裁决。",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.ancient": "呵呵……真是令人战栗的正义感。只需付出小小的代价，你就可以拥有我的力量，去执行更彻底的审判。",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "又见面了。正义的齿轮转动得太慢，不如签下这份简便的契约，让一切瞬间如你所愿？",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.ancient": "只需交出一点点微不足道的权限……这很划算，不是吗？",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0.next": "回应",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.char": "可笑的契约。恕我无法在这份废纸上签字。",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1.next": "继续",
  "VAKUU.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2.ancient": "啧……竟然被识破了吗。那就按普通的规矩来吧。这些够“正常”了吗？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.ancient": "你来了，异邦的审判者。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-0.next": "回答",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.char": "你的行径已严重偏离公正，自诩「规则」之人。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-1.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-2.char": "在宣告判决前，我允准你对高塔中的指控进行申辩。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-2.ancient": "真是令人不安的力量……",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-2.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.0-3.ancient":"离开吧，审判者，此地之事与你无关。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.ancient": "啧，又是你。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-1r.char": "正义当使恶者受罚，善者得偿。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-2r.ancient": "恶者吗……哈。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-2r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.1-3r.ancient": "就让我这个「恶者」，将你送回塔底吧。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0r.ancient": "你在怜悯我吗？审判者？",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-0r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1r.char": "此事如有冤屈，我自会秉公裁决。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-1r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2r.char": "……不妨告知于我。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-2r.ancient": "……",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-3r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-3r.ancient": "伟大如你，不必插手此事。",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-4r.next": "继续",
  "THE_ARCHITECT.talk.NEUVILLETTE_CHARACTER_NEUVILLETTE.2-4r.ancient": "回去吧，审判者。"
}
